Hitpoints_Max_Total.formula: Max((Hitpoints_Max + Hitpoints_Max_Bonus) * (1 + Hitpoints_Max_Percent_Bonus) * (1 + Hitpoints_Max_Percent_Bonus_Item) * (1 + Hitpoints_Max_Percent_Bonus_KeyDun) + TableHealthFromFlat(Flat_Hitpoints_Max_Bonus, Level), 0.01)
Hitpoints_Max_Total.name: Hitpoints_Max_Total

Movement_Scalar_Subtotal.formula: Max(0.1, Movement_Scalar) * (1 + Movement_Bonus_Total) * (1 - Movement_Scalar_Reduction_Percent * (1 - Min(1, Movement_Scalar_Reduction_Resistance)))
Movement_Scalar_Subtotal.name: Movement_Scalar_Subtotal
